óŸOarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/history.mdŸ@80111caba7446a169adf81959a698d0b6a2deb6a8bde0937b4625c5205d5f470Ætitle: historyë®Examples⁄êGet current history length
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> history | length


```
Show last 5 commands you have ran
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> history | last 5


```
Show last 5 commands with full details
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
